flowRoot.flowPara: Research is sometimes like a puzzle that can be put together in more than one way. Others need to know how you put the puzzle together, not just what the pieces are.
Research is more than conclusions. It starts with a question. That question leads to another. Eventually a clear picture emerges. But it's the journey that's important.
We believe life is too short to redo other people's research. We can move faster and build better research conclusions as we build on each others research. No man is an island.
Our flagship product, Geungle, is a genealogical research system. Built upon industry standards, it is awesome.
Ever struggled with research? Tired of having to redo or check other peoples' research? Wish it wasn't so hard to share your work? We build software that makes research easier.
